==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rapper
<hw>Rap"per</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧p"p⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Rap</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, raps or
knocks; specifically, the knocker of a door.</def>
<rj><au>Sterne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A forcible oath or lie.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>
<rj><au>Bp. Parker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A musician specializing in <er>rap
music</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rapport</ent>⟦br⟧
